you are looking for. 

You quickly find the examination office on the top floor of the building, and \
fortunately for you, whoever is working at the moment has left his workstation \
and left the door unlocked. You tell Josie and John to please stand guard. You \
sit down at the PC and see the login window. You know very well that this PC \
will not be locked for much longer.

