Now you have to cover your tracks. You delete the search entry from the search \
history of the database, move all windows on the PC as they were before, lock \
the PC and leave the office with John and Josie. Just as you disappeared around \
the next corner, you could hear footsteps, probably moving from the other end \
of the hallway toward the exam office. If you had taken a little longer, you \
would have been caught. 

You leave the building and towards the car.

